        <title>Availability and implementation</title>
        <p><ext-link xlink:href="https://github.com/lorrainea/Seedability" ext-link-type="uri">https://github.com/lorrainea/Seedability</ext-link> (distributed under GPL v3.0).</p>
      </sec>
